{"tid":275420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港府研究重組輕鐵路線 10年內將路軌與馬路分開","createTime":"2017-06-08T04:25:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T04:31:37.000Z","uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"683a2deb343cfe706e9ca4a869bebb7b90f8ee1b","tid":275420,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:25:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/sy/ny/api/res/1.2/Y34tnaAxAEGC1Irbq72RQA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20170608a100726.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2Fsy%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FY34tnaAxAEGC1Irbq72RQA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20170608a100726.jpg&h=f0662032&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】政府發表《公共交通策略研究》結果，當中提到如何改善元朗等新界地區的交通。<br />\n<br />\n運輸署長楊何蓓茵在電台節目中表示，為了解決元朗大馬路擠塞問題，短期會將輕鐵路線重組及合併，並會明年首季前，更換交通燈的控制晶片，令輕鐵列車運行更暢順，紓緩擠塞情況。她又說，政府與多間巴士公司接觸，他們都有興趣在新界推出不設企位的長途豪華巴士來往市區，當局亦曾做過調查，居民願意支付較高票價使用這些服務。巴士公司稍後會設計路線，並在地區試驗。<br />\n<br />\n運輸及房屋局副秘書長陳帥夫亦表示，為了解決輕鐵與汽車爭路問題，會研究如何將路軌與馬路分開，但改道問題大費周章，估計需要5至10年時間。當局亦會研究是否興建鐵路，由新界直接出市區，希望未來會像港島北，有電車及地鐵疏導人流。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E9%87%8D%E7%B5%84%E8%BC%95%E9%90%B5%E8%B7%AF%E7%B7%9A-10%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%A7%E5%B0%87%E8%B7%AF%E8%BB%8C%E8%88%87%E9%A6%AC%E8%B7%AF%E5%88%86%E9%96%8B-013300384.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%25B5%2584%25E8%25BC%2595%25E9%2590%25B5%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E7%25B7%259A-10%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%25B0%2587%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E8%25BB%258C%25E8%2588%2587%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E5%2588%2586%25E9%2596%258B-013300384.html&d=Cw2PUvMBpwLuQPtG7jJqAm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=8aeecfeb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E9%87%8D%E7%B5%84%E8%BC%95%E9%90%B5%E8%B7%AF%E7%B7%9A-10%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%A7%E5%B0%87%E8%B7%AF%E8%BB%8C%E8%88%87%E9%A6%AC%E8%B7%AF%E5%88%86%E9%96%8B-013300384.html</a>"},{"pid":"e045aafda17d3a812d204d33e4f965fe512010a3","tid":275420,"uid":34202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:29:04.000Z","msg":"大馬路嗰道分開就啱 但搞嗰陣啲交通&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de44f75ea68cb4c0e9a3785e9cfbb5c38dcb8cee","tid":275420,"uid":50595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:30:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大馬路嗰道分開就啱 但搞嗰陣啲交通&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搞搞個迴旋處啦"},{"pid":"7e5e82f86bcda3b9e1dce28703897cad5c99a135","tid":275420,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:31:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大馬路嗰道分開就啱 但搞嗰陣啲交通&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁你想點 整點都有影響架啦"}]}